    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works made of woven, coiled, inscribed, or carved bamboo, which is material derived from woody or treelike tropical and semitropical grasses of various genera.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
